I'm drinking water.

15:17.017 --> 15:19.286
I mean, this might not be
significant to you guys,

15:19.319 --> 15:20.887
but I can't even remember
the last time

15:20.920 --> 15:22.722
-I had a bottle of...
-That is so good to hear.

15:22.755 --> 15:25.125
It makes me feel good, but we
are in a bit of a time crunch,

15:25.158 --> 15:26.726
-so I'm gonna hang
onto this guy. -Mickey!

15:26.759 --> 15:28.095
-Huh? Hmm?
-What the hell's wrong with you?

15:28.128 --> 15:29.262
What? He can have water.
You can have water

15:29.296 --> 15:30.463
when you're done with the job.

15:30.497 --> 15:31.564
She's right. A deal's a deal.

15:31.598 --> 15:33.266
-Right?
-All right. Okay, fine.

15:33.300 --> 15:35.468
-You know what you're doing,
right? -I think so.

15:35.502 --> 15:37.104
All right, any minute,
Barry's gonna leave for work.

15:37.137 --> 15:39.072
You're gonna follow him,
he'll pull to a stop.

15:39.106 --> 15:40.940
