he's banging dudes.

15:48.815 --> 15:50.917
-SABRINA: Mm-hmm.
-This is a great plan.

15:50.950 --> 15:52.986
Aah! He's early.

15:53.020 --> 15:55.022
-Go get 'em.
-Wish me luck.

15:55.055 --> 15:56.889
