of speed limits?

16:04.497 --> 16:06.633
It seems fast. I'm not sure
that thing's even gonna...

16:07.734 --> 16:09.102
-Whoa!
-Oh!

16:09.136 --> 16:10.670
MICKEY:
And there goes the money.

16:12.372 --> 16:14.707
