16:18.345 --> 16:20.013
-Ho. Ho. Ho. I got you.
I got you. -Oh.

16:20.047 --> 16:21.814
-MICKEY: He's mostly staying
conscious. -You okay?

16:21.848 --> 16:23.983
-But they... they did meet.
-Uh.

16:24.017 --> 16:25.618
Wow.

16:25.652 --> 16:28.521
You're... beautiful.

16:28.555 --> 16:30.957
(giggles)
Uh...

16:30.990 --> 16:32.525
MICKEY:
Hmm.

16:32.559 --> 16:34.294
SABRINA:
Holy crap. I think it's working.

16:34.327 --> 16:37.630
Of course it's working.
It's a great plan.

16:37.664 --> 16:39.899
No. You're dead. Stop.
Just get him, get him.

16:39.932 --> 16:41.834
-You get... get him.
-Excuse me.

16:41.868 --> 16:45.672
-Can I help you gentlemen with
something? -Nah, we're good.

16:45.705 --> 16:48.341
You don't mind
if I see a room key, do you?

16:48.375 --> 16:50.077
Yeah...

16:50.110 --> 16:52.045
(inhales sharply)
Must've left it in my pants.

16:52.079 --> 16:54.881
Oh, no problem. What's the name
on the reservation?

16:54.914 --> 16:57.084
I'd rather not say.

16:57.117 --> 16:58.551
And why is that?

17:00.587 --> 17:03.156
I don't feel comfortable giving
my name out to strangers.

17:03.190 --> 17:05.425
All right, look, fellas,

17:05.458 --> 17:08.228
