That's my mistake.

17:33.220 --> 17:35.255
What can I do to make it right?

17:35.288 --> 17:38.057
Well, look who decided
to show up to work.

17:38.091 --> 17:40.893
You could start
by giving me a towel. Now!

17:40.927 --> 17:43.763
Right away.
I'm very sorry.

17:43.796 --> 17:45.532
I'm sorry about that, boys.

17:45.565 --> 17:47.066
World's full of idiots.

17:47.100 --> 17:48.768
