18:07.120 --> 18:09.322
-(Alba laughs)
-Mmm. -Ooh. -Yeah?

18:09.356 --> 18:13.426
-Mmm! Kumamotos on point
tonight. -JIMMY: Yeah...

18:13.460 --> 18:14.827
-(all laugh) -Hey,
have another one. Have 'em all.

18:14.861 --> 18:16.296
-It's your day.
