littlest bit of my respect.

18:28.040 --> 18:30.343
Look, I am just glad
we are out of the Courtship.

18:30.377 --> 18:31.944
-Am I right? -Yes. -Yes.
-JIMMY: Oh, yeah.

18:31.978 --> 18:33.513
