18:33.546 --> 18:34.947
-To the Fairbanks.
-MICKEY: Yes!

18:34.981 --> 18:37.350
-Fairbanks! -Fairbanks!
-(all cheering)

18:37.384 --> 18:38.785
-Ooh, it's Barry!
-Barry!

18:38.818 --> 18:40.187
-(all cheering)
-No, no, no, no.

18:40.220 --> 18:42.855
