19:34.441 --> 19:36.309
That is my sister and her kids.

19:36.343 --> 19:37.744
I've been living with them

19:37.777 --> 19:39.946
since their father was killed
in Afghanistan.

19:43.850 --> 19:45.818
Mmm...

19:45.852 --> 19:47.420
Mm-hmm, mm-hmm.

19:47.454 --> 19:50.156
Uh-huh.

19:50.189 --> 19:52.559
Well.

19:52.592 --> 19:56.996
If you will all excuse me
for a moment,

19:57.029 --> 20:00.467
